metadata.title: GEEKRIA Audio Cable Compatible with Bose QuietComfort SE QCSE QC45 QuietComfort35 II QC35 QC25 700ANC NC700 Cable, 2.5mm Replacement Stereo Cord (4 ft / 1.2 m)
features: Made of premium copper provide optimal conductivity and durability.
Thermoplastic Elastomer (TPE) and rugged, ensure the superior audio transfer against electron magnetic or radio interference (EMI or RFI), extreme cold or hot temperature and maximum protection.
Work with devices with standard 3.5mm AUX jack, such as headphone amplifier, MP3 players, laptops, PCs, cellphones, tablets, home theaters, speakers, game console controllers, PS4, PS5, Switch, etc.
Package includes: 1 x headphones replacement cable with 2.5mm jack.
Cable compatible with Bose Headphones-700 NCH700 NC700 QC45 QC35-II QC35 QC25 QuietComfort45 QuietComfort35 QuietComfort25 headphones cable.
description: - Compatible with Bose QuietComfort SE, QC SE, QCSE cable - Compatible with Bose QC 45, QC35 II, QC35, QC25 cable - Compatible with Bose QuietComfort 45, QuietComfort 35 Series II cable - Compatible with Bose QuietComfort 35, QuietComfort 25 cable - Compatible with Bose Noise Cancelling Headphones 700, NCH 700, NC 700 cable and more 2.5mm port headphones.
